test.doc: 1. Open demo.parstream.com 2. Open Airports tab 2.1 Verify that Airports tab is opened 3. Open Best Direct Flight Search tab 3.1 Verify that 'Open Best Direct Flight Search tab' is opened 4. Click on the 'Reset' button 5. Select part on the 'Top Airlines' pie 6. Select part on the 'Top Airports' pie 7. Select 'Average Delay bu Day' chart 8. Select 'Average Taxi' chart 9. Select 'Average Delay by Quarter' chart 10. Navigate to 'Best Direct Flight Search' 11. Set From and To states 12. Extend the Year range 12.1 Verify that page is reload
